{"tid":906692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抑鬱）【突然死亡】工程學院黨委書記李耀東 辦公室自縊身亡","createTime":"2018-11-18T08:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T08:23:08.000Z","uid":40628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2b8d6215ab73d39c5c138a74ec2bd1c4eab949d","tid":906692,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181113/58909581\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181113%2F58909581&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=336ae383\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181113%2F58909581&h=9f6dd7f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181113/58909581</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181113/large/1542111714_bdee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181113%2Flarge%2F1542111714_bdee.jpg&h=6600a318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑龍江工程學院官網發佈公告，稱昨日(12日)下午，該學院黨委書記李耀東被發現在辦公室自縊身亡，經公安現場勘查取證，排除他殺。<br />\n<br />\n李耀東1963年8月出生，黑龍江哈爾濱人，中共黨員，學士，於2018年2月任職黑龍江工程學院黨委書記。李耀東曾擔任黑龍江省廣播電視局副局長、黨組成員、副總編輯，七台河市委常委、宣傳部長，黑龍江省第四批援藏工作隊領隊，西藏日喀則地委副書記、行署常務副專員等職務。"},{"pid":"6ebd608d1c4de9ef40326df08c583d4c39600077","tid":906692,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:17:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d05fbc694eb3f407645961af14176136258dcea","tid":906692,"uid":205396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:20:48.000Z","msg":"肯撚定被人查到貪污<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef47af02c5269be58dc5482ff780830cbc81497","tid":906692,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:21:55.000Z","msg":"幾時到李國章盧寵茂抑鬱?"},{"pid":"f0095c04d43499fada3582a1ae5cec7a495e3d6f","tid":906692,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:23:08.000Z","msg":"香港啲鳩官咁大壓力<br />\n幾時先抑鬱"}]}